r-streaming flows with the certain width\nalong the threads of solar filaments exist and are well coaligned with the\nthreads.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Feb 2015 05:46:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-14"}
